content: Hello, I'm trying to attend office hours via Zoom and am able to enter the queue. However, it keeps resetting to where I need to enter the zoom link again and I am entered at the end of the queue. Does this mean that the queue is being locked because OH is too full, or is this a glitch on my end?
subject: Zoom Office Hour Isses

content: I would check to make sure there isn't a password on your zoom link, or that it is otherwise valid. If an LA claims you and can't connect to your zoom, there's no way to contact you about it and they'll need to prioritize others that are in person.
